<h1>Add your project</h1>

<h2>1. Generate your project link</h2>

<p>
  <strong>Your project's repository url:</strong>
  <%= text_field_tag :project_url, nil, placeholder: 'github.com/username/project', id: 'project_url_input' %>
</p>

<button type="link" id="button">Generate project link ‚Üì</button>

<pre id="link">Your link will appear here!</pre>

<h2>2. Copy and paste the link on another tab for testing</h2>

<p>You can try this link in another tab before you share it.</p>

<h2>3. Share the link</h2>

<p>Now your users can contribute to your project by donating hashes and you can earn Monero.</p>

<p>
  <a id="link2" href="" target="_blank"></a>
</p>

<script>
  var link = document.getElementById('link')
  var link2 = document.getElementById('link2')
  var button = document.getElementById('button')
  var project_url_input = document.getElementById('project_url_input')

  button.addEventListener('click', function() {
    var ready_url = "<%= ENV['ROOT_URL'] %>/project?url=" + project_url_input.value

    link.innerHTML = ready_url
    link2.innerHTML = ready_url
    link2.href = ready_url
  })
</script>

